"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n          \"reason\": \"Hermetic tests can exercise descriptor/version resolution against a temporary file:// Maven repository without live network access, but Resolver needs a file transporter implementation for that.\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"agent_guidance\": \"Use a temporary local repository/session and a temporary file:// remote repository with minimal POM/metadata fixtures. Configure the RepositorySystem from MavenRepositorySystemUtils.newServiceLocator(), register the available connector/transport services, and set a LocalRepositoryManager rooted in a temp directory. Avoid live Maven Central/network resolution. Avoid covering MavenResolverModule unless explicit Guice/Guava optional dependencies are intentionally added.\",\n      \"risks\": [\n        \"Without connector and transport implementations, tests that call RepositorySystem resolution APIs will fail with missing connector/transporter services rather than exercising this provider.\",\n        \"The public MavenResolverModule class references optional Guice classes that are not part of the normal transitive runtime classpath; generated tests should avoid it unless additional optional dependencies are added.\",\n        \"HTTP transport is not included because hermetic tests should use file:// repositories; tests that choose live HTTP resolution would need org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-transport-http:1.9.25 and would be less reliable.\"\n      ],\n      \"applied_setup\": [\n        {\n          \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n          \"coordinate\": \"org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-connector-basic:1.9.25\",\n          \"result\": \"applied\",\n          \"target\": \"tests/src/org.apache.maven/maven-resolver-provider/3.9.12/build.gradle\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n          \"coordinate\": \"org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-transport-file:1.9.25\",\n          \"result\": \"applied\",\n          \"targ